{"tid":2027574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我發覺獨立宣言、憲章太多，大家要揀到岩用既先得","createTime":"2020-05-21T12:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T13:04:19.000Z","uid":154486,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2caa5a956686ebe926920fac527d211c7b3a710d","tid":2027574,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:26:18.000Z","msg":"見到有兩位巴絲出post講宣言同憲章<br />\n<br />\n係支那國安法正式開始所謂立法工作既時候，香港獨立既構思更加要同時開展<br />\n<br />\n我地有好多好多個版本既宣言同憲章<br />\n每一個都相當令人振奮<br />\n當然每一個都有人有意思<br />\n<br />\n但係最終大家都要歸納成一個或者幾個簡約既草案<br />\n以下係最近既兩份宣言<br />\n<br />\n【521香港獨立宣言】集合所有人力量 今晚九點前我要所有人睇過！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2027177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2027177</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n四月憲章<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1964084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1964084</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n加上呢一個曾經宣讀過既<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AE%A3%E8%A8%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25A8%2580&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoV5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=07859cd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AE%A3%E8%A8%80</a><br />\n<br />\n宣言最終最重要係廣泛既認受性同埋權威性<br />\n而家冇錯冇乜可能可以揾到大人物支持<br />\n<br />\n但係唔代表我地唔可以寫好D﹐寫清楚D﹐寫現實D﹐寫簡潔D"},{"pid":"18c996bc59b27ce30d6c781a5387479af8aa8777","tid":2027574,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"幫自己推post"},{"pid":"26ebc289eba512218717bb8ba0916d53c4c486b5","tid":2027574,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"推post推post推post"},{"pid":"852ee58c1b5dfc0bd407788f731668f88fbaa9ae","tid":2027574,"uid":154486,"like